OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cstabbing outside school in Birmingham
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched in Alum Rock, in Birmingham,
OL,8,Fafter a man died following a stabbing
OL,9,Foutside of a primary school today (3
OL,10,FMarch).
OL,12,FWest Midlands Police were called to
OL,13,FBridge Road at 12.06pm following a
OL,14,Freports a man had been seriously
OL,15,Finjured.
OL,17,FThe police has now confirmed a man in
OL,18,Fhis 20s has died.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
