OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cstabbing outside school in Birmingham
OL,6,FA 32-year-old man has been arrested in
OL,7,Fconnection with the stabbing and
OL,8,Fremains in police custody. A woman
OL,9,Falso sustained injuries not believed
OL,10,Fto be life threatening or changing.
OL,12,FWest Midlands Police said a number of
OL,13,Ffirearms officers both uniformed and
OL,14,Fplain clothed attended. They confirmed
OL,15,Fthis was routine for this type of case
OL,16,Fand that it's not being treated as
OL,17,Fterrorism related.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
