OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cstabbing outside school in Birmingham
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent James Munro
OL,7,Ffrom West Midlands Police, said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts remain with the man's family
OL,9,Fat this time.
OL,11,F"We believe this to be a contained
OL,12,Fincident with a man in custody.
OL,14,F"We are reviewing CCTV footage and
OL,15,Fspeaking to a number of people in the
OL,16,Farea. But would appeal to anyone who
OL,17,Fhas any information to get in touch.
OL,26,@oD@bOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
